'''scaffolding'''
#A [[temporary]] [[modular]] [[system]] of [[metal]] [[tube]]s forming a [[framework]] used to [[support]] [[people]] and [[material]] in the [[construction]] or [[repair]] of [[building]]s and other large [[structure]]s.  The framework may also be made of [[bamboo]] or [[wood]].

